description: Sound quality is typically not associated with the ubiquitous ear bud. The CX890i changes this. It’s a high resolution in-ear canal design that presents your favorite music like you’ve never heard before. The sound is crystal clear, with a smooth and natural response. The style is distinctive as the performance. A combination of metal and glass like material give the CX890i outer shell a sophisticated look that compliments it’s premium overall finish. A custom fit is achieved with three different sizes of ear adaptors. The correct fit ensures optimum performance while blocking distracting ambient environmental noise. Control of Apple products such as the iPad, iPhone or iPod is accomplished with a cable employing an integrated smart remote with microphone. This is used to adjust volume, select tracks, take phone calls and activate the voice control feature. The CX890i’s 32-ohm operating impedance and 3.5-mm stereo jack mean this headphone is optimized for premium performance and connectivity to any “I” device. Step up to premium in-ear performance with the CX890i.
title: Sennheiser CX 890i Headset (Black) (Discontinued by Manufacturer)
